02:18.670 --> 02:20.371
Mrs. Matheson?

02:20.373 --> 02:22.105
Who're you?

02:22.107 --> 02:24.208
I'm Detective Scarpelli.

02:24.210 --> 02:25.375
I've been assigned to your husband's case.

02:25.377 --> 02:27.711
Why're you here? What is this about?

02:27.713 --> 02:29.213
I'm here to place you under arrest, ma'am.

02:29.215 --> 02:30.480
What?

02:30.482 --> 02:31.815
You can't do this here!

02:31.817 --> 02:34.384
Guys don't. We knew this could happen.

02:34.386 --> 02:37.120
Call Karen Lescher, then Uncle Rob.

02:37.122 --> 02:38.888
- Mom...
- It's going to be fine.

02:38.890 --> 02:39.922
Luke, take your sister home.

02:39.924 --> 02:41.725
We're coming with you, all right?

